reviews.content: I have been dissapointed by the lack of professionalism by the staff.  One time my nurse had headphones in. Several times the office staff has made mistakes that resulted in me having to come back in, resulting in additional copays.  I.e. one nurse argued when I said the Dr. Needed urine, causing me to have to come back.  . Doctor spent no more than 5 min with me each visit and seemed reluctant to diagnose.  Long wait times and office staff discuss other patients right next to the waiting room. . For the amount I pay my insurance company the quality of service was a let down.
